===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} ''[[fuiret]]'' (modern ''[[furet]]'') < {{LL.}} ''[[furo]]'' ‘thief, ferret’, diminutive of {{etyl|la}} ''[[fur#Latin|fur]]'' ‘thief’.

