*: {{rhymes|ɛrɪt}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[mammal]] rather like a [[weasel]], but which was originally bred from the [[polecat]] and often trained to [[hunt]] [[rat]]s or [[rabbit]]s in [[England]].

